title: 142. Creating Loyalty For Success
itunes:title: 142. Creating Loyalty For Success
description: What does loyalty mean to you? On today's episode, Andy debunks the idea that loyalty is how long you've known someone, defines what loyalty actually entails and how being loyal to yourself can open up tremendous opportunities for you.
